<div id="review_589905" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/589905" />
    <a title="Amy Deringer" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/49438-amy-deringer"><img alt="Amy Deringer" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1617627220p2/49438.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/589905?book_show_action=true">Apr 05, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amy Deringer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amy Deringer" href="/user/show/49438-amy-deringer">Amy Deringer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780396081593" href="/book/show/241990.The_Father_Brown_Omnibus">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/49438-amy-deringer?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer589905" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18002696328680065687">The omnibus is the exhaustive collection of G.K. Chesterton&apos;s Father Brown short stories. If you&apos;ve got a taste for detective stories and clever, British tones, then you&apos;ll love it. The omnibus is huge and I&apos;ve been working through it for about 8 months. Take it a story at a time with a cup of hot tea and low lighting!</span>
  <span id="freeText18002696328680065687" style="display:none">The omnibus is the exhaustive collection of G.K. Chesterton's Father Brown short stories. If you've got a taste for detective stories and clever, British tones, then you'll love it. The omnibus is huge and I've been working through it for about 8 months. Take it a story at a time with a cup of hot tea and low lighting!</span>
