        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2729594470" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10685092963106689530">Such wonderful stories.<br/>We watched the tv series and was hooked on it so had to get the complete stories obviously<br/>This book is the type you need on a winters day in a country pub with an open fire -snuggled in the inglenook. It reads like an old friend without ever reading it before (I know that doesn&apos;t make sense but it almost hugs you with the warmth of the writing).<br/>Love this book - it will defiantly be one of my forever favourites!</span>
  <span id="freeText10685092963106689530" style="display:none">Such wonderful stories.<br />We watched the tv series and was hooked on it so had to get the complete stories obviously<br />This book is the type you need on a winters day in a country pub with an open fire -snuggled in the inglenook. It reads like an old friend without ever reading it before (I know that doesn't make sense but it almost hugs you with the warmth of the writing).<br />Love this book - it will defiantly be one of my forever favourites!</span>
